            "accordion_row_HqHKCA": {
              "type": "_accordion-row",
              "settings": {
                "heading": "What bag sizes does your popcorn come in?",
                "open_by_default": false,
                "icon": "none",
                "width": 20
              },
              "blocks": {
                "text_ihXn6z": {
                  "type": "text",
                  "settings": {
                    "text": "<p>Our bag sizes are in volume, not packed by weight, and we do our best not to sell air.😀 We’ve got a bag for every kind of craving!</p><ul><li>Mini Munch (3 cups): A tiny taste of popcorn joy.</li><li>JV Munch (6 cups): JV in size, but a Varsity starter in taste. Perfect for sharing with a friend.</li><li>Small Munch (11 cups): A solo snack or movie-night favorite you can share.</li><li>Medium Munch (32 cups): Great for family game nights or small gatherings.</li><li>Large Munch (Coming Soon).</li></ul><p>All our munch-size bags are heat-sealed for freshness and  reclosable. No matter the occasion, Milton’s Popcorn has a bag that’ll make your moment pop!</p>",
                    "width": "100%",
                    "max_width": "normal",
                    "alignment": "left",
                    "type_preset": "custom",
                    "font": "var(--font-body--family)",
                    "font_size": "0.875rem",
