            },
            "accordion_row_896zir": {
              "type": "_accordion-row",
              "settings": {
                "heading": "What if I need to return or exchange something?",
                "open_by_default": false,
                "icon": "none",
                "width": 20
              },
              "blocks": {
                "text_MA8CxH": {
                  "type": "text",
                  "settings": {
                    "text": "<p>Since every batch is made fresh and ready to munch, we can’t offer refunds or exchanges once your order is placed. Didn’t love a flavor? Try our Mini Munch Bags next time—they’re perfect for sampling! If your order arrives damaged or incorrect, contact us right away. We’ll make it right with a replacement, discount, or store credit—because every kernel counts at Milton’s Popcorn!<br/><br/><a href=\"https://e3q1y7-wg.nyla.site/_web_preview/pages/contact-us\">Contact Us</a></p>",
                    "width": "100%",
