                  "type": "text",
                  "settings": {
                    "text": "<p>Uh-oh! Sometimes boxes take a bump along the way—but don’t worry, we’ll fix it fast. Email us a quick photo of the damage so we can get things sorted right away. Thanks for your patience—we’ll make sure your next batch arrives picture-perfect and ready to crunch!<br/><br/><a href=\"https://e3q1y7-wg.nyla.site/_web_preview/pages/contact-us\">Contact Us</a></p>",
