              "blocks": {
                "text_wbcJyp": {
                  "type": "text",
                  "settings": {
                    "text": "<p>We ship Monday through Friday, and most orders head out within 3 business days. You can choose your favorite carrier (UPS or FedEx) at checkout—just note we can’t refund those charges once booked. Need it fast? Pick Express, 2-Day, or Overnight Shipping at checkout. Warm Weather Tip: Meltable goodies travel best with 2-Day or Overnight Shipping, which includes free cold packs! And don’t forget—once shipped, address changes cost $20, so double-check before you click “Place Order.”</p>",
